    <h1>PASTA</h1>
    <h2>Recipe of the Pasta</h2>
<p>This is my favourite food. Let's learn the recipe!</p>
<p><strong>Ingredients</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li>Pasta</li>
    <li>Capsicum</li>
    <li>Onion</li>
    <li>Tomatoes</li>
    <li>Ginger</li>
    <li>Garlic</li>
    <li>Green Chilli</li>
    <li>Cooking Oil</li>
    <li>sauce</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Instruction</strong></p>
<ol>
    <li>Boil Pasta</li>
    <li>Heat the cooking oil</li>
    <li>Add ginger,garlic and green chilli paste</li>
    <li>Then add onion,capsicum and saute  till until golden brown</li>
    <li>Add salt and sauce</li>
    <li>Then add cooked pasta ,mix it well</li>
</ol>
